<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Thank You!</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:300,400|Montserrat:700" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #343a40;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .site-header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .site-header__title {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .main-content {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px auto;
            max-width: 600px;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .main-content__checkmark {
            color: #28a745;
            font-size: 4em;
        }

        .main-content__body {
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        .site-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .site-footer__fineprint {
            font-size: 0.8em;
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="site-header">
        <h1 class="site-header__title">THANK YOU!</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="main-content">
        <i class="fa fa-check main-content__checkmark"></i>
        <p class="main-content__body">Thanks a bunch for filling that out. It means a lot to us, just like you do! We really appreciate you giving us a moment of your time today. Thanks for being you.</p>
    </div>

    <footer class="site-footer">
        <p class="site-footer__fineprint">Copyright ©2024 | All Rights Reserved</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
